rComments: Awesome prof; very enthusiastic about teaching , knows the course well and really encourages questions from the class.
Super helpful when you need assistance. Be prepared to work. You learn a lot if you put the time and effort into the class. I learned a lot about climate that I didn't know before.

The man is scary enthusiastic about this course! He's very passionate and engaging, sorta makes you depressed about the future, but this is a good course to take! Prepare to study a lot though there's a ton of material he goes over. Go to lectures!!
